    "As well, ML algorithms are developed and applied for detecting food taste; thus serving as an electronic tongue (Pallante et al., 2022).",
    "In short, AI has found its application from genomics to phenomics for devising appropriate data analytics (van Dijk et al., 2021), which could be further exploited for ensuring higher crop yields and sustainable agriculture.",
